&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Providing young professionals with access to the most in-demand tech skills that will power the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Empowering the next generation of technology innovators, entrepreneurs, and business leaders through challenging, real-world coursework.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Building a lifelong, impactful community of tech professionals that support them at all stages of their career journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
