&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Business Development &amp;amp; Partnerships Associate will drive the day-to-day execution of ALX Ethiopia&#39;s three BD workstreams, Corporate Training, Ecosystem Partnerships, and Fundraising &amp;amp; Philanthropy, under the direction of the BD &amp;amp; Partnerships Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own outbound pipeline activity, qualify leads to Sales Qualified Lead (SQL) standard, write and submit proposals and concept notes, manage active deal documentation, and maintain the pipeline tracker across all three workstreams. You will also support the BD Manager in coordinating the BD task force, a team of part-time contributors working across the three revenue streams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will not close deals alone. You will make sure every deal that should close has everything it needs to move forward, and that nothing is stuck because of a missing document, an unsent follow-up, or an untracked conversation.&lt;/p&gt;
